INSTALLING gslimp3
==================

Requirements
------------

  * python
  * python-gtk2
  * python-glade2
  * madplay (or another MPEG player)
  * an up and running SlimServer accessible on your network. SlimServer is
    downloadable from the Slim Devices web site:
    http://www.slimdevices.com/

Install
-------

  $ su -c "make install"

Run
---

  $ gslimp3
